citation: Education and Training (Tasmanian Skills Institute) Act 2008 (Repealed) (Tas)
text:
Education and Training (Tasmanian Skills Institute) Act 2008 (Repealed)

1. (Repealed)
    The Education and Training (Tasmanian Skills Institute) Act 2008 has been repealed by Schedule 2 to the Training and Workforce Development (Repeals and Consequential Amendments) Act 2013
